{"tid":680163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"銀行無出過數紙收錢方話check唔到過數紀錄可以點","createTime":"2018-05-27T04:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T06:06:56.000Z","uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc27f708c7815d71f1a3b976f9dbc094a2e70ae","tid":680163,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的 ，本身訂咗枱食放題 （幫公司訂） ，要比＄500訂金。<br />\n我就星期五經中銀機過數（但佢無哂紙所以出唔到過數紙） ，已經即時打去客服到問 ，條友竟然話「如果冇紙你唔好入呀嘛？！」。我撚知會無紙 ？<br />\n<br />\n到星期六 ，我直接殺去中銀問 ，叫佢比返個過數紀錄我 ，佢話要排隊申請 ，時間答唔到我。<br />\n<br />\n我就打去放題間野到 ，佢話會計部check唔到尋日晚數 ，只睇到即日數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話我拎唔到過數紙個按金咁係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我開網上銀行睇  ，佢只有過數日子同銀碼 ，無過數户口 ，即是我拎比間餐廳都唔會認數。<br />\n<br />\n係呢個情況下 ，我想問有咩方面係星期三前攞到個過數紀錄 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6437b623d49b7e0b6415bfe5879b13f37248e151","tid":680163,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fc27f708c7815d71f1a3b976f9dbc094a2e70ae","tid":680163,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的 ，本身訂咗枱食放題 （幫公司訂） ，要比＄500訂金。<br />\n我就星期五經中銀機過數（但佢無哂紙所以出唔到過數紙） ，已經即時打去客服到問 ，條友竟然話「如果冇紙你唔好入呀嘛？！」。我撚知會無紙 ？<br />\n<br />\n到星期六 ，我直接殺去中銀問 ，叫佢比返個過數紀錄我 ，佢話要排隊申請 ，時間答唔到我。<br />\n<br />\n我就打去放題間野到 ，佢話會計部check唔到尋日晚數 ，只睇到即日數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話我拎唔到過數紙個按金咁係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我開網上銀行睇  ，佢只有過數日子同銀碼 ，無過數户口 ，即是我拎比間餐廳都唔會認數。<br />\n<br />\n係呢個情況下 ，我想問有咩方面係星期三前攞到個過數紀錄 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係月結單係寄信嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都等唔到咁耐 ⋯"},{"pid":"364d5b29533633903d5bc4d84d27479b040cf15c","tid":680163,"uid":32544,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"比多次訂金，解決左餐飯先，事後再查番銀行記錄拎番$500訂"},{"pid":"de48b7ac8bb7d4473694201c40ea73820ed0d590","tid":680163,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:29:12.000Z","msg":"🙊🙊🙊🙊🙊🙊🙊🙊🙊"},{"pid":"c422d6aed10f418777944526862e2a9cbd53b4ac","tid":680163,"uid":43731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"可以叫銀行出返張atm單比你，需時大約兩星期，你唯有同餐廳講如果拎得返張單返來退500$比你，如果大集團都好d, 細個d你當買左個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa0176253c69472078c291ba45faf77bd5ac330","tid":680163,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c422d6aed10f418777944526862e2a9cbd53b4ac","tid":680163,"uid":43731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"可以叫銀行出返張atm單比你，需時大約兩星期，你唯有同餐廳講如果拎得返張單返來退500$比你，如果大集團都好d, 細個d你當買左個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"但算大集團 好多間分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我點知佢部機會係紙咁有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23379f1d442166672ae86517902a6a74228c47d3","tid":680163,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04: